---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About ResonantOS and ResonantDAO" description="ResonantOS is the shared system; ResonantDAO is the membership and governance layer that lets the community steward it.">
	<section class="px-4 pb-16 pt-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
			<p class="mb-5 font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-400">About</p>
			<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-6xl">A philosophy, a system, and a DAO.</h1>
			<p class="mt-8 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-8 text-zinc-300">
				ResonantOS has evolved. The current work is to connect the philosophical foundation of Augmentatism with a practical DAO membership system that can govern, protect, and co-own the shared work.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Augmentatism</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">The shared discipline for cultivating conscious, sovereign collaboration with AI and technology.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">ResonantOS</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">The shared system, architecture, and body of work the community is building around.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">ResonantDAO</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">The membership, governance, contribution, and co-ownership layer for the ResonantOS ecosystem.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">The First Practitioner</h2>
			<p class="mt-4 text-zinc-400">
				The project began as a live experiment led by Manolo Remiddi at the intersection of human creativity, AI, governance, and public building. The next stage is to turn that experiment into a community-owned structure with explicit credentials and rules.
			</p>
			<a href="https://manoloremiddi.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="mt-6 inline-block text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300">manoloremiddi.com</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
